@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
[*] --> Created
Created --> Draft : process
Created : entry / log user
Draft --> Completed : approve
Completed --> Reviewed : review
Completed : entry / log user
Reviewed --> OnHold : confirm
OnHold --> Cancelled : confirm
OnHold : entry / log user
Cancelled --> [*]
@enduml